column3: Oh, hello! I didn't see you there.
Doing some interior decorating.  It's kind of drab in here...
What are you? What brings you here?
Oh, yes. We get a lot of wanderers here. Lots and lots and lots of 'em.
People come and go.  You know how it is.
That's sweet of you, but he's probably busy.  [REDACTED] is such a busy man. I can pass along a message if you like.
